57}, {\"ngram\": \"stuff\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was always so good at recall.\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1126, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"recall\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I got through a law degree basically just by going, 'Ah, page 32, Smith versus Cook'.\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1212, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a law degree\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1153}, {\"ngram\": \"Cook\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was always good with names, finding the right word at the right time, and I'd find myself umming a bit or using 'very, very, very'..\\\", reportsWales Online.\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1370, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"names\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1241}, {\"ngram\": \"the right word\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1265}, {\"ngram\": \"the right time\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1283}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Then, when I realised it was a symptom of perimenopause, it was actually a relief, like it normally is when you realise something is part of a process and you can do something about it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a symptom\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"perimenopause\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1430}, {\"ngram\": \"a relief\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1456}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1504}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1512}, {\"ngram\": \"a process\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1525}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1550}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gabby has taken a leap \\\"reading outside of her comfort zone\\\", which includes writing an entire book titled 'The Midpoint plan', exploring the theme of healthy living in middle age.\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1743, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gabby\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1568}, {\"ngram\": \"a leap\", \